          "url": "https://github.com/Iron-Mark/Iron-Mark/blob/main/public/FAQ.md#what-is-mark-siazons-tech-stack-answer"
        },
        "text": "Mark Siazon's core stack is React, Next.js, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS for web; Flutter and Kotlin for mobile; Python and Supabase on the backend; and Figma for design, with Stellar and Celo for Web3. Full 113-tool reference: https://github.com/Iron-Mark/Iron-Mark/blob/main/public/STACK.md",
